description: Dreamcakes Bakery is taking their delicious & beautifully decorated selection of cupcakes through all of Birmingham, courtesy of their big ‘ole Cupcake Truck. Named “the best little cupcake in Alabama” by Birmingham News, this award winning selection of famous flavors includes Caramel Sea Salt Mocha, Chocolate Cheesecake, Peaches N’ Cream, Birthday Cake, and many more. For these special cupcakes, custom cakes, oatmeal cream pies, and French macaroons too, you just gotta come by the Cupcake Truck (or invite them to come cater your dream wedding or next big fest) and enjoy a few of these sweet frosted fantasies come true.
name: Dreamcakes Cupcake Truck
